{"article_id":"84pkVVUFtvOjNBV8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin left little doubt Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that the administration will reject a congressional request for President Donald Trump 's tax returns by a self-imposed May 6 target for a `` final decision , ''","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"setting the stage for a legal battle","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that will test the limits of congressional oversight .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"In a 10-page letter to House Ways and Means Chairman Richard Neal","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"( D-Mass . ) ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"who formally requested Trump 's returns on April 3 ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Mnuchin questioned Neal 's motives","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and laid out `` some of the legal concerns ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"the administration has with the request .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"While Neal has argued","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that the committee needs to see the returns as part of its oversight of the IRS ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Mnuchin wrote","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that is a \" pretext \" for the Democrats ' aim","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to make Trump ' s returns public ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"which Mnuchin called \" constitutionally suspect . \"","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Neal ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"who had set a 5 p.m. Tuesday deadline","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"for the IRS to turn over the documents ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that he plans to `` consult with counsel about my next steps. \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"He is likely to subpoena the documents at some point","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"given the administration ' s resistance to subpoenas","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"issued or threatened by other committees ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"the dispute is expected to wind up in court .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Mnuchin 's letter reads like a legal brief in many places .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"It includes two appendices and nearly three dozen footnotes ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"mostly citing media reports about the dispute and press releases from Democrats , along with transcripts of statements","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"they made ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"about plans","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to publicly disclose Trump ' s tax returns .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"It reinforces assumptions","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that the administration will challenge the request on grounds","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that Neal has no legitimate legislative or policy purpose","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"for seeking them .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Neal is invoking a law","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that allows the chairs of the two congressional committees with tax jurisdiction to examine anyone 's tax returns .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Ways and Means needs to be able to vet IRS audits of the president ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"he has said ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"though Democrats also make no secret of their desire","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"to examine Trump 's returns for evidence of possible financial malfeasance and other wrongdoing .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"Sign up today","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"In an April 13 letter to IRS Commissioner Chuck Rettig , Neal said","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"the request for Trump 's returns `` falls squarely within the Committee ' s oversight authority . ''","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"He cited 10 judicial precedents on the matter","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that the Supreme Court has time and again reaffirmed the legislative branch 's role .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"The Trump administration has now missed two deadlines","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"set by Neal","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"for turning over the returns .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Mnuchin told Neal on the first deadline day two weeks ago","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that Treasury needed more time","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to examine the issue","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and was consulting with the Justice Department .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Neal then reupped his request .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"He could write yet another letter","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"threatening to use any and all powers","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"available to him","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"to get the administration to comply ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"followed by a subpoena for Trump 's returns .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"Several administration officials , and Trump himself , have said","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Congress wo n't get the documents .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Frustration is building within the House Democratic caucus .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"On Monday , Rep. Jared Huffman","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"( D-Calif. )","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"House Democrats should consider impeaching Rettig .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Though Neal 's requests for the returns have gone directly to the IRS commissioner ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Mnuchin has taken the lead on the issue ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"which Democrats say","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"is a violation of normal procedure .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Rettig sent a separate letter to Neal on Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"the Justice Department ' s examination of the issue is \" beyond the scope of internal revenue laws . \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" Accordingly , we have not made a final determination","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"on how to respond to your request","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and are awaiting further guidance and direction ...","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"before doing so , \"","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Rettig wrote .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Earlier Tuesday , White House spokesman Hogan Gidley indicated","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that the administration would reject the request for Trump 's returns ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"repeating the president 's claim","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that he ' s being audited by the IRS","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"as the reason","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"he wo n't release them .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"`` As I understand it ,","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"the president 's pretty clear :","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Once he 's out of audit ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"he 'll think about doing it ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"but he 's not inclined to do so at this time , ''","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Gidley told Fox News .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"`` It 's already been litigated in the court of public opinion and in the election .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"The president won it fairly and squarely , ''","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"`` He 's the president ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"and no one cares about ridiculous charges about tax returns and all types of other things","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Democrats are doubling down on today . ''","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"If the administration ultimately rejects the request for Trump 's returns ,","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"as expected ,","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Neal plans to build a court case against the decision as a violation of the Administrative Procedure Act , a law","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"that governs the actions of federal regulatory agencies like the IRS","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"and that has been successfully deployed in other cases against the Trump administration .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Neal is n't the only committee chairman","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"the administration is defying .","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"Trump is suing House Oversight Chairman Elijah Cummings","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"( D-Md . )","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"to block a subpoena of Trump ' s financial records from an accounting firm , Mazars USA .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"Cummings wants the bank records to investigate allegations","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"that Trump falsely inflated and deflated asset values","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"to benefit himself ,","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"but the president ' s lawyers have said","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"House Democrats are abusing their power","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"to try to embarrass Trump .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":172,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":163,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":125,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":146,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":136,"right":145,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":130,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":128,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":6,"relat